        "folder": "bowl_bbq_and_fun_night_2019",
        "date": "2019-08-05",
        "description": "On Saturday 3rd August, over 60 members and friends enjoyed our second annual “Bowl, BBQ and Fun Night” to raise funds for the Club’s 2021 Centenary. The weather didn’t match last year’s sunshine, but everyone still played a few ends before the rain came. Our dedicated BBQ team served over 100 people, and the night ended with games, raffles, a quiz, and prizes for the first visitor to get a “chalker” and the top rink. Thank you to everyone who came and helped make it a great success!",

