    {
        "name": "Opening of the Greens for Season 2018",
        "folder": "opening_of_the_greens_2018",
        "date": "2018-04-15",
        "description": "The greens opened on Friday 13th April. Despite the chilly weather, 16 members and guests played 5 ends. Claire McGroarty, daughter of Gents' President John McGroarty, delivered the silver jack and impressively got a toucher with her first ever bowl! The flag was raised by Honorary President Matt Paul and Executive Chair Moira Bryan. Afterwards, everyone enjoyed hospitality in the hall. The opening dance on Saturday 14th featured vocalist Andy Sommers and a fish supper. The Centenary Group raffle draw raised £111, with John Forbes winning 6 bottles of spirits — congratulations, and thank you to everyone who bought tickets!",

